snippet.title: Planet 51 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The official video game of the movie is here! As Planet 51 makes its way to theaters across the world this Thanksgiving holiday, the game is arriving right beside it for the DS, Wii, Xbox 360, and PS3! 

For even more information about Planet 51, check out our website at www.planet51game.com !
